279
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:08,500
Seguro.

280
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:09,270
Bueno.

281
00:13:09,270 --> 00:13:09,900
La madre de Wanzhe.

282
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:11,240
¿Has visto a Hong?

283
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:12,030
¿Hong?

284
00:13:12,050 --> 00:13:13,270
¿Por qué lo buscas?

285
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:14,110
